1
00:01:10,919 --> 00:01:11,480
Slow down.

2
00:01:12,519 --> 00:01:13,040
Sister Lin.

3
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:13,680
Sister Lin.

4
00:01:14,839 --> 00:01:15,279
Senior.

5
00:01:15,839 --> 00:01:16,319
Gao Ming.

6
00:01:16,319 --> 00:01:16,919
What did you find?

7
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:19,000
We found a phone at Tan Feng's.

8
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:21,040
If we can confirm this phone is Du Zheng's,

9
00:01:21,519 --> 00:01:22,319
