158
00:06:54,359 --> 00:06:55,920
The mastermind behind the Raw Material Case

159
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,640
and the suspect

160
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:58,519
who killed Du Zheng

161
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,480
are very likely the same person.

162
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,239
What's more coincidental is that

163
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:03,880
the suspect, Tan Feng,

164
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,279
during the time of the crime,

165
00:07:05,839 --> 00:07:07,480
only contacted one person, and that was you.

166
00:07:08,399 --> 00:07:09,600
Before Du Zheng died,

167
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,679
the last person he saw was also you.

168
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:15,200
Feng Ziang,

169
00:07:16,119 --> 00:07:17,040
tell me,

170
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,920
why is this exactly?

171
00:07:19,799 --> 00:07:20,920
Are you saying

172
00:07:22,239 --> 00:07:24,200
the mastermind behind this raw material incident

173
00:07:24,519 --> 00:07:25,239
is me?

174
00:07:26,679 --> 00:07:27,440
And that

175
00:07:27,839 --> 00:07:29,480
I killed our best brother?

176
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:32,119
Based on the current situation,

177
00:07:33,119 --> 00:07:34,959
I can only make such an assumption.

178
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,160
You're right, Officer Lin.

179
00:07:40,359 --> 00:07:41,480
You said it yourself,

180
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,679
this is your assumption.

181
00:07:43,519 --> 00:07:45,119
Do you realize you are falsely accusing me?

182
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:46,760
Please investigate

183
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:47,839
my financial transaction records.

184
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:50,359
If I were the mastermind behind this incident,

185
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,760
then I would have made a fortune,

186
00:07:52,359 --> 00:07:52,920
right?

187
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,079
Also,

188
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,720
if you don't believe I was simply

189
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,239
helping the company handle this matter,

190
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:58,160
then I can

191
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,359
give you the handling plan for this incident,

192
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,119
the meeting minutes,

193
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,519
and the company's internal investigation reports.

194
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,679
That way, the phone's origin and user

195
00:08:06,239 --> 00:08:07,079
will be clear to you, right?

196
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,559
Du Zheng was my best buddy.

197
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:13,040
If you want to accuse me of murdering him,

198
00:08:13,959 --> 00:08:15,239
please show me the evidence.

199
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,600
Officer Lin,

200
00:08:17,079 --> 00:08:18,559
I feel very uncomfortable

201
00:08:19,679 --> 00:08:21,079
with these baseless accusations of yours.

202
00:08:32,599 --> 00:08:34,080
Freshly brewed coffee,

203
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,479
and I had to leave just like that.

204
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:38,320
Are you messing with me?

205
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:41,679
I should have drunk it before I left.

206
00:08:54,719 --> 00:08:55,280
What's wrong?

207
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:56,599
The Chairman is missing.

208
00:08:56,880 --> 00:08:57,559
What?

209
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,440
This is all your doing.

210
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:02,440
He was already dying.

211
00:09:02,719 --> 00:09:04,200
How could you be so ruthless?

212
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,960
Take a look.

213
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:07,919
Are you satisfied now?

214
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:14,799
Tiancheng.

215
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,719
I will not let you

216
00:09:16,919 --> 00:09:18,000
or anyone else

217
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:20,200
who wants me dead get their way.

218
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,760
For twenty years,

219
00:09:22,359 --> 00:09:24,359
rather than as a husband and father,

220
00:09:24,479 --> 00:09:26,359
I have been living more as

221
00:09:26,359 --> 00:09:27,359
the Chairman of Feimanchi.

222
00:09:28,159 --> 00:09:30,679
I am the brain and heart of this company.

223
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:34,000
I will never step down from this position.

224
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:36,760
No matter what threats you use,

225
00:09:37,559 --> 00:09:39,320
I will never back down.

226
00:09:42,719 --> 00:09:43,440
Chairman!

227
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:51,599
Chairman!

228
00:09:54,479 --> 00:09:56,880
I know you want revenge on me.

229
00:09:57,559 --> 00:09:58,679
But if you want to drag

230
00:09:58,679 --> 00:10:00,280
all of Feimanchi down with you,

231
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,080
I will never allow it.

232
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:05,599
I'd rather die than let you get your way.

233
00:10:10,520 --> 00:10:11,280
Gu Rongchen!

234
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:15,039
Gu Rongchen!

235
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,400
Who said you could die?

236
00:10:48,760 --> 00:10:49,719
Gu Rongchen!

237
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,760
Is this position that important?

238
00:10:54,359 --> 00:10:55,719
So important that you'd abandon

239
00:10:55,719 --> 00:10:56,960
your loved ones and family?

240
00:10:57,919 --> 00:10:58,599
Gu Rongchen!

241
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,039
Get up!

242
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:01,719
Mr. Gu,

243
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:03,599
please calm down.

244
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:07,039
The Chairman is already gone.

245
00:11:38,119 --> 00:11:39,200
What are you looking at?

246
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:43,719
I'm checking to see if you're okay.

247
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:47,200
Wondering if your successful revenge

248
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:48,840
has brought you extreme sorrow.

249
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:51,640
Are you done looking? Let's go.

250
00:11:53,039 --> 00:11:54,280
No, you look too depressed.

251
00:11:55,039 --> 00:11:56,320
Have you been holed up here all day?

252
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,520
Alright, I'll stop joking with you.

253
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:04,479
Since things have come to this,

254
00:12:04,919 --> 00:12:06,679
everything has come to an end.

255
00:12:07,359 --> 00:12:09,320
I don't know if you're satisfied with this ending,

256
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,239
but

257
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,679
you should probably let it go now.

258
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:15,559
The funeral...

259
00:12:16,280 --> 00:12:17,000
How was it?

260
00:12:23,919 --> 00:12:24,919
I thought

261
00:12:26,119 --> 00:12:27,919
the Chairman of a large enterprise...

262
00:12:28,599 --> 00:12:30,200
I originally thought that when he passed,

263
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,559
it would be a grand affair.

264
00:12:31,559 --> 00:12:32,840
There would be many people to see him off.

265
00:12:33,679 --> 00:12:34,559
But I never expected

266
00:12:35,559 --> 00:12:36,719
that at the memorial service,

267
00:12:36,719 --> 00:12:38,200
fewer than twenty people showed up.

268
00:12:40,679 --> 00:12:41,960
I finally saw

269
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:44,640
what it means when rats abandon a sinking ship.

270
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,400
Gu Rongchen ending up like this today

271
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:51,359
is entirely his own fault.

272
00:12:52,880 --> 00:12:54,159
It was when he was developing the enterprise

273
00:12:54,159 --> 00:12:55,039
that he harbored selfish motives

274
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:55,960
and mismanaged it.

275
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:58,599
He also deliberately hid his illness

276
00:12:59,239 --> 00:13:00,119
and didn't get proper treatment.

277
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:03,119
But he

278
00:13:03,640 --> 00:13:05,039
paid for it with his life, didn't he?

279
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:06,679
He probably wouldn't think

280
00:13:06,679 --> 00:13:08,239
that the things he did were wrong.

281
00:13:13,599 --> 00:13:14,200
What's wrong with you?

282
00:13:14,919 --> 00:13:15,880
My heart feels a bit uncomfortable.

283
00:13:16,119 --> 00:13:16,840
I'll call Dr. Duan right now.

284
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:17,880
No need.

285
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:20,000
I just took my medicine.

286
00:13:20,719 --> 00:13:21,599
I'll be fine after resting for a bit.

287
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,000
Could you look into something for me?

288
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:25,119
Tell me.

289
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:28,440
My heart donor...

290
00:13:29,479 --> 00:13:30,119
Who exactly are they?

291
00:13:30,239 --> 00:13:31,280
What?

292
00:13:31,760 --> 00:13:32,799
No way.

293
00:13:33,239 --> 00:13:34,599
Hospitals have confidentiality agreements.

294
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:36,280
I'm telling you, this is illegal.

295
00:13:36,520 --> 00:13:38,400
That's why I'm asking you to investigate secretly.

296
00:13:38,880 --> 00:13:39,359
No,

297
00:13:39,919 --> 00:13:40,479
no.

298
00:13:40,479 --> 00:13:42,000
What if I do find out?

299
00:13:44,599 --> 00:13:45,679
Just consider it

300
00:13:47,359 --> 00:13:48,280
as me begging you.

301
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:52,919
I'm begging you, bro.

302
00:13:53,559 --> 00:13:54,400
Is that enough?

303
00:13:57,479 --> 00:13:59,960
You, Mr. Gu Tiancheng, are actually begging me?

304
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:02,840
The sun must be rising in the west.

305
00:14:05,400 --> 00:14:06,479
Just for this...

306
00:14:06,479 --> 00:14:07,520
groveling attitude of yours,

307
00:14:08,239 --> 00:14:09,039
I agree to do it.

308
00:14:10,159 --> 00:14:10,960
I didn't expect

309
00:14:11,239 --> 00:14:12,760
Director Feng to make such a sudden move.

310
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:13,640
He's amazing.

311
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,359
Why are you still calling him Director Feng?

312
00:14:15,640 --> 00:14:16,799
You should call him Mr. Feng now.

313
00:14:16,799 --> 00:14:17,559
If we had known this day would come,

314
00:14:17,559 --> 00:14:19,159
we should have sucked up to him earlier.

315
00:14:19,359 --> 00:14:20,880
Who could have thought he'd be where he is today?

316
00:14:21,359 --> 00:14:22,640
Back when Chairman Gu was around,

317
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,359
look at how submissive he was.

318
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,039
Hello, Chairman.

319
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:34,280
Hello, Chairman.

320
00:14:36,119 --> 00:14:37,159
Everyone, go back to work.

321
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:41,760
Jiaqi.

322
00:14:48,479 --> 00:14:49,119
Congratulations, sir.

323
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:49,960
What's with the "sir"?

324
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:51,080
Jiaqi,

325
00:14:51,799 --> 00:14:52,760
don't play this game with me.

326
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:55,320
Business is business, personal is personal.

327
00:14:55,479 --> 00:14:57,280
I still have to respect you in the company.

328
00:14:58,280 --> 00:14:58,840
Alright.

329
00:14:59,400 --> 00:15:00,039
Suit yourself then.

330
00:15:06,239 --> 00:15:06,760
Jiaqi,

331
00:15:07,359 --> 00:15:08,359
are these all for him to review?

332
00:15:08,719 --> 00:15:09,280
Yes.

333
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:10,640
He hasn't arrived yet?

334
00:15:10,799 --> 00:15:11,960
No.

335
00:15:12,719 --> 00:15:13,880
This guy is unbelievable.

336
00:15:14,159 --> 00:15:15,559
Skipping work for no reason.

337
00:15:17,119 --> 00:15:18,280
Still can't reach him?

338
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:20,559
His phone is turned off.

339
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:21,479
He's pulling a disappearing act.

340
00:15:21,760 --> 00:15:22,359
How about this?

341
00:15:22,640 --> 00:15:23,520
I'll try to contact him.

342
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:24,840
Jiaqi,

343
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:25,559
I'll leave it to you then.

344
00:15:26,119 --> 00:15:26,919
I'll get back to work then.

345
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:45,679
You need to attend

346
00:15:45,679 --> 00:15:46,479
the Vice Minister of Finance's

347
00:15:46,479 --> 00:15:47,679
entrepreneur symposium.

348
00:15:48,119 --> 00:15:49,479
When will you be back?

349
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:01,520
Tomorrow is the 25th.

350
00:16:02,359 --> 00:16:03,200
I think

351
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:04,440
I must remind you,

352
00:16:05,239 --> 00:16:07,000
shouldn't you go to Wanshou Shan?

353
00:16:16,400 --> 00:16:17,919
What did you say? Feng Ziang is pursuing you?

354
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:19,960
Keep your voice down. Why are you so excited?

355
00:16:20,400 --> 00:16:21,760
Are you planning to date him?

356
00:16:22,679 --> 00:16:23,799
How is that possible?

357
00:16:23,799 --> 00:16:25,000
We're buddies.

358
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:29,159
You don't like him, do you?

359
00:16:29,799 --> 00:16:31,280
Lin Jiaqi, are you kidding me?

360
00:16:31,280 --> 00:16:32,119
I...

361
00:16:32,719 --> 00:16:34,440
Then why, when I told you he was pursuing me,

362
00:16:34,440 --> 00:16:35,479
were you so excited?

363
00:16:35,880 --> 00:16:36,880
But honestly,

364
00:16:37,280 --> 00:16:38,280
you two are quite a good match.

365
00:16:38,559 --> 00:16:40,479
You... are you being serious?

366
00:16:41,599 --> 00:16:42,559
Anyway, right now, you two

367
00:16:42,559 --> 00:16:43,559
just can't be together.

368
00:16:44,479 --> 00:16:46,400
Crazy. I already said it's impossible.

369
00:16:46,880 --> 00:16:47,919
Can you come to my house?

370
00:16:50,239 --> 00:16:50,960
What's wrong?

371
00:16:51,359 --> 00:16:52,280
I have to stand you up.

372
00:16:52,799 --> 00:16:53,679
No way.

373
00:16:53,679 --> 00:16:54,919
We just started our date.

374
00:16:55,159 --> 00:16:56,359
The big boss is summoning me.

375
00:16:56,359 --> 00:16:58,520
As a sidekick, I can only obey.

376
00:16:59,679 --> 00:17:01,479
I'm actually quite glad there's this big boss.

377
00:17:01,640 --> 00:17:02,359
What's wrong?

378
00:17:04,040 --> 00:17:04,520
Nothing.

379
00:17:05,160 --> 00:17:05,560
All right.

380
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:06,640
I won't nag you anymore.

381
00:17:06,800 --> 00:17:07,400
I'm leaving first.

382
00:17:08,079 --> 00:17:08,800
You pay the bill.

383
00:17:09,199 --> 00:17:09,920
Got it.

384
00:17:10,640 --> 00:17:11,439
Be careful on the road.

385
00:17:37,239 --> 00:17:38,359
I couldn't reach you all this time.

386
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:39,839
We were all very worried.

387
00:17:43,359 --> 00:17:44,599
What's there to worry about me?

388
00:17:46,560 --> 00:17:47,520
I thought

389
00:17:47,959 --> 00:17:49,199
the Chairman's matter

390
00:17:50,680 --> 00:17:51,560
would affect you.

391
00:17:54,719 --> 00:17:56,040
That matter, to me,

392
00:17:56,040 --> 00:17:57,239
has no effect at all.

393
00:17:58,119 --> 00:17:59,119
You guys are overthinking.

394
00:18:01,199 --> 00:18:02,040
Come to think of it,

395
00:18:02,800 --> 00:18:04,359
I haven't taken a vacation in over ten years.

396
00:18:06,280 --> 00:18:06,839
Then,

397
00:18:07,359 --> 00:18:08,599
are you well-rested now?

398
00:18:11,439 --> 00:18:12,199
Today,

399
00:18:14,839 --> 00:18:15,760
come with me.

400
00:18:16,719 --> 00:18:17,280
Me?

401
00:18:18,199 --> 00:18:18,839
Yes.

402
00:18:19,760 --> 00:18:20,640
Come to think of it,

403
00:18:21,560 --> 00:18:22,760
weren't you the one who reminded me?

404
00:18:40,199 --> 00:18:41,359
I brought Uncle's

405
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:43,239
favorite light-aroma baijiu,

406
00:18:43,599 --> 00:18:45,160
and Auntie's favorite pastries.

407
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:49,119
Let's chat with them.

408
00:19:08,160 --> 00:19:09,119
Dad.

409
00:19:11,079 --> 00:19:11,880
Mom.

410
00:19:13,239 --> 00:19:14,119
I'm here.

411
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:20,959
I came too late.

412
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:25,920
Will you blame me?

413
00:19:30,199 --> 00:19:31,199
It's been twenty years.

414
00:19:36,920 --> 00:19:38,680
I finally fulfilled what I promised you

415
00:19:41,800 --> 00:19:43,760
in my heart twenty years ago.

416
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:49,520
Do you think your son is great?

417
00:19:53,719 --> 00:19:54,640
All these years,

418
00:19:56,439 --> 00:19:58,000
I've always been alone,

419
00:19:59,599 --> 00:20:01,040
living for profit.

420
00:20:03,280 --> 00:20:04,280
I'm so tired.

421
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:12,160
What did you chat about with Uncle and Auntie just now?

422
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:13,520
Nothing much.

423
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:19,760
Watch out!

424
00:20:27,959 --> 00:20:28,839
It's just a small animal.

425
00:20:31,040 --> 00:20:31,599
Let's go.

426
00:20:37,160 --> 00:20:38,079
The engine won't start.

427
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:42,319
What's going on?

428
00:20:42,319 --> 00:20:43,000
Is the battery dead?

429
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:44,479
I don't know.

430
00:20:45,160 --> 00:20:45,880
I'll go down and check.

431
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:46,800
Is it broken?

432
00:20:50,400 --> 00:20:50,959
How is it?

433
00:20:51,239 --> 00:20:52,239
What's the problem?

434
00:20:52,719 --> 00:20:53,640
Call the car dealership service.

435
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:08,119
It's going to rain.

436
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:09,479
Get in the car quickly.
